Consider that each node of the tree is a structure with the following ﬁelds:
(cid:73) key: the useful information of the node;
(cid:73) color: red / black;
(cid:73) pred: the address of the parent node (null for the root);
(cid:73) left: the address of the left child;
(cid:73) right: the address of the right child.
